<h2>Windows Installation Notes</h2>
<p>The Velocity installer will install Velocity to %USER_HOME%\Program Files\Velocity by default on Windows
operating systems. This is primarily to avoid problems with the Windows Vista User Account Control (UAC) which does not
allow applications to write to the Program Files folder without elevated privileges (using the administrator account).</p>
